mealDesc: How we dream about our future.
mealDetails: A meal is an eating occasion that takes place at a certain time and includes prepared food.[1][2] The names used for specific meals in English vary, depending on the speaker's culture, the time of day, or the size of the meal.Meals occur primarily at homes, restaurants, and cafeterias, but may occur anywhere. Regular meals occur on a daily basis, typically several times a day. Special meals are usually held in conjunction with such occasions as birthdays, weddings, anniversaries, and holidays. A meal is different from a snack in that meals are generally larger, more varied, and more filling than snacks.
